      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>The following settings are available in the module settings panel. These settings are world-scoped and apply to all users in the world.</p><h2 class=\"custom-dnd5e-h2\">Max Ability Score</h2><p>Sets the maximum ability score a character can have. The default value is 20. Increasing this value allows ability scores to exceed the normal cap, which may be useful for epic-level campaigns or homebrew rules.</p><h2 class=\"custom-dnd5e-h2\">Max Level</h2><p>Sets the maximum character level allowed. The default value is 20. This can be increased for campaigns that extend beyond the standard level range.</p>"
      },
